{"tid":1458806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說散水撚 試著說擔心撚","createTime":"2019-08-12T15:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:37:31.000Z","uid":24356,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ad1c6bbbcfe98aa6b3ab984900d3fd35bd6cb5","tid":1458806,"uid":24356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"大家嘅初心都一樣<br />\n因為今日有好多流言 大家都好擔心同伴嘅安全<br />\n所有人都只係想齊上齊落<br />\n唔好再有被捕！<br />\n<br />\n現場嘅同伴可以講多謝大家關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c931962f753e5441c932e4c0ea867337199441","tid":1458806,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用下個腦諗嘢，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n你哋唔好喺度發文喺度煽動<br />\n佢地成功分化我地了啦<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本效益的）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"54542eb4414aa4257569596e52d31b7e5da1d370","tid":1458806,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"555e8e339dde0b8988b42a9aa6437a989d943498","tid":1458806,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"66d5cf6d56feb7231ebcf9252003a8a59109e6c2","tid":1458806,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"[賽後檢討] 抗爭者進化史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13b4e871ecb46c9ff0227d41541c918e800be418","tid":1458806,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"正面"},{"pid":"0817c90971b62589223394fda2615427e07c3078","tid":1458806,"uid":118488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"推，分化由此起"},{"pid":"fe34a657640ff9c52afc63415fcf29d8c9ca3ff7","tid":1458806,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">機場keep 住和理</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武keep 住搵仔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各有各做，兄弟爬山</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"9c48bada7fde9f5c91d9f67b3568f06b7496d249","tid":1458806,"uid":24356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"不分化 不指責"},{"pid":"d9c8c6ee37964620c09bb18dbb6fc9